Module frogger
Package frogger.service

Class MapFactory

  • java.lang.Object
    • frogger.service.MapFactory
  • public class MapFactory
extends java.lang.Object

    MapFactory

    The MapFactory class is used to generate a Map depend on the given gameLevel by calling MapReader

    Note: this class is implemented as an factory pattern.

    Main Functionality: 

                    MapFactory.createMap(MapType);

    Use: 

                    MapFactory.{method}(); (Static Method Only)
    Since:
    1.0
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Wenzheng Shan
    See Also:
    Map, MapReader
